4 Laws 2023, sections 1, 2, 3 and 12, chapter 630, Oregon Laws 2025, and sections 3, 7, 11 and 20,
5 chapter 633, Oregon Laws 2025; repealing section 37, chapter 633, Oregon Laws 2025; and de-
6 claring an emergency.
